1. *Kaži* meni svoju istinu! (Tell me your truth!)
2. Znam da ćeš *kaži* da si srećan! (I know you'll say you're happy!)
3. *Kaži* mi zašto si to učinio! (Tell me why you did that!)
4. Ona je *kažala* da je ljubomorna na njega. (She said she was jealous of him.)
5. Šta ćeš *kažati* na njegovu izjavu? (What will you say to his statement?)
6. On je *kažao* da je vreme da se oprostimo. (He said it's time to say goodbye.)